{"an4.17:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 4.17 ","an4.17:0.2":"2. Caravagga ","an4.17:0.3":"Pathamaagatisutta ","an4.17:1.1":"“Cattarimani, bhikkhave, agatigamanani. ","an4.17:1.2":"Katamani cattari? ","an4.17:1.3":"Chandagatim gacchati, dosagatim gacchati, mohagatim gacchati, bhayagatim gacchati—","an4.17:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, cattari agatigamananiti. ","an4.17:2.1":"Chanda dosa bhaya moha, ","an4.17:2.2":"yo dhammam ativattati; ","an4.17:2.3":"Nihiyati tassa yaso, ","an4.17:2.4":"kalapakkheva candima”ti. ","an4.17:2.5":"Sattamam. "}